 has taken an uncannily similar decision. We used to believe that BRAC University accommodates all religious views and practices and evaluates its students according to their merit. However, this recent decision has gone against such an image of BRAC University and instead has expressed the apparent anti-Islamic bigotry that has so far only been exhibited by Fascist Far-right parties in the West. Furthermore, this problem could have been solved by keeping female guards to check the female students who have chosen to wear Niqab. However, according to our knowledge, you don\u2019t want to take this step (a step which can protect a girl\u2019s modesty, respect her religious duty and ensures her freedom of expression) due to \u201cincreased costs\u201d We wonder, why an institution such as BRAC University, would find it difficult to employ a few (or even one) female guard(s) for female students.\n\nWe are aware of the fact that you have not given any written notice to the students yet, regarding their wearing of the face veil. Therefore, we kindly request you to clarify your position (and dispel the rumors) officially by Saturday. We hope that BRAC University will live up to its reputation and give us a decision in favor of students practicing their faith, something which every human being holds dearly.\n\nStudents of BRAC University","picture":"https:\/\/fbcdn-photos-d-a.akamaihd.net\/hphotos-ak-frc3\/1000802_487605407994095_2102383508_s.jpg"}